engniu Dairy|Yoyic]]\n|Brand Ambassador\n|January 28, 2019\n|Yes\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.weibo.com/2048734302/He0lCn5p0|title=\u4f18\u76caC\u5fae\u535a|last=|first=|date=January 28, 2019|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=January 28, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Master Kong]]\n|Green Tea Brand Ambassador\n|March 13, 2019\n|Yes\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.weibo.com/3231479672/HkHDOv4ZG|title=\u5eb7\u5e08\u5085\u7eff\u8336|last=|first=|date=March 13, 2019|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=March 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Youku]]\n|VIP Member Spokesperson\n|April 11, 2019\n|No\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.weibo.com/1940275640/Hp72aqqCF|title=\u4f18\u9177VIP\u4f1a\u5458\u5fae\u535a|last=|first=|date=April 11, 2019|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=April 11, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[\u00c9vian|Evian]]\n|Global Brand Ambassador\n|May 16, 2019\n|Yes\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BxgxZqsIalH/|title=evian instagram|last=|first=|date=May 16, 2019|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=May 16, 2019}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.weibo.com/1808574132/HuqpPCDAn|title=evian\u4f9d\u4e91\u4e2d\u56fd\u5fae\u535a|last=|first=|date=May 16, 2019|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=May 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[https://www.ximalaya.com/ Ximalaya]\n|APP Brand Ambassador\n|June 11, 2019\n|Yes\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.weibo.com/2608693591/HynwKwGGV|title=\u559c\u9a6c\u62c9\u96c5\u5fae\u535a|last=|first=|date=June 11, 2019|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=June 11, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Rimowa|RIMOWA]]\n|Brand Spokesperson for China\n|June 25, 2019\n|Yes\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.weibo.com/5470353808/HAyAGel6Y|title=RIMOWA\u65e5\u9ed8\u74e6|last=|first=|date=June 25, 2019|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=June 25, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Adidas O